data.description: Southwest Colony at Copake Lake. This 2 BR, 1 BA has been updated with a new floor plan. New appliances, wrap-around deck, attached garage and both an attic and basement. Located a little off the lake offers you a quieter setting, yet this home is just a short distance away to lake and dock access.Copake Lake is the largest recreational lake in Columbia County and is centrally located between Hudson, NY and Great Barrington, MA. Near to Copake Country Club (public 18 holes with farm-to-table Greens Restaurant), organic farms, skiing, aerial park, zip line, Harlem Valley Bicycle Path, theatre, music, Tanglewood, antiquing and restaurants galore. MetroNorth and Amtrack are also nearby. About a 2 hour drive from New York in southern Southern Columbia County.
